    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub collects the document's punctuation and typographic devices. The dominant mark is the **em-dash**, used across children as a rhetorical pivot and payoff-amplifier ([assertion—correction cadence](narr:StyleObs_EmDashRhetoric), [claim—consequence amplifier](narr:StyleObs_DashAsAmplifier), [inline clarifying definitions](narr:StyleObs_EmDashDefinition), [pause-and-emphasis detail](narr:StyleObs_EmDash_1)), and as the essayistic signature of the pitch voice ([list-unpacking em-dashes](narr:StyleObs_5)). The **arrow (→)** appears as process-flow shorthand ([group-interview flow](narr:StyleObs_ArrowNotation)) and as directional framing with bold labels ([bold+arrow+claim](narr:StyleObs_BoldArrowFraming)). **Bold** ranges from conviction-stress ([substitutive 'replaces'](narr:StyleObs_SMB_BoldEmphasis), Mar 2026) to scannable navigation ([beat headers](narr:StyleObs_BoldBeats), [role-category labels](narr:StyleObs_BoldEmphasis)). Further devices: [italic contrastive stress](narr:StyleObs_ItalicsForEmphasis), [scare-quotes for category disruption](narr:StyleObs_ScareQuotes), [checkmark-emoji validation](narr:StyleObs_Checkmark_Validation), [fenced code-block architecture](narr:StyleObs_CodeBlockArchDiagram), [parenthetical term-glosses](narr:StyleObs_ParenthesisGloss), [all-caps 'IS' stress](narr:StyleObs_2), and [three-word declaratives / antithesis](narr:StyleObs_3).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ;
